description: Lists the calling Amazon Web Services account's dedicated origination numbers and their metadata. For more information about origination numbers, see Origination numbers in the Amazon SNS Developer Guide.

nested_items.name: NextToken
nested_items.description: A NextToken string is returned when you call the ListOriginationNumbers operation if additional pages of records are available.

nested_items.name: PhoneNumbers
nested_items.description: A list of the calling account's verified and pending origination numbers.

nested_items.name: CreatedAt
nested_items.description: The date and time when the phone number was created.

nested_items.name: Status
nested_items.description: The status of the phone number.

nested_items.name: Iso2CountryCode
nested_items.description: The two-character code for the country or region, in ISO 3166-1 alpha-2 format.

nested_items.name: NumberCapabilities
nested_items.description: The capabilities of each phone number.
(string) --- Enum listing out all supported number capabilities.
